profile:
Your driveway is cleared for every snowfall of 5 cm or more. Our professional operators make a return visit to clear away the City of Ottawa plow debris and keep your driveway clear. During major snow storms, our professional operators make extra visits to keep you moving in and out of your driveway during heavy snowfalls. 

We are 24/7 on-call service & we guarantee snow removal services 24/7, including holidays. We offer extra packages that include walkway snow removal services upon request.

All our snow blowers are equipped with tyvar plastic cutting edges to minimize damage to interlock and landscaped surfaces.

No Snow Maximum Amount
